gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Nuggets 130, Wizards 110
gameRecap.excerpt: The Nuggets defeated the Wizards, 130-110. Nikola Jokic recorded his 16th triple-double this season (21 points, 19 rebounds, and 15 assists) for the Nuggets, with Michael Porter Jr. adding 22 points and 11 rebounds in the victory. Kyle Kuzma tallied 31 points and 13 rebounds for the Wizards in the losing effort. The Nuggets improve to 37-19, while the Wizards fall to 9-46.
